Wendy Craig https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wendy_Craig 0 Anne Gwendolyn Craig (born 20 June 1934), known professionally as Wendy Craig, is an English actress who is best known for her appearances in the sitcoms Not in Front of the Children, Butterflies, ...And Mother Makes Three and ...And Mother Makes Five. She played the role of Matron in the TV series The Royal (2003–11).
